    <view class="ad-content-box">
      <p class="ad-content ad-content-margin">
        <text space="emsp"> “普惠微贷”是深圳农商银行为个体工商户、小微企业量身订造的，用于短期生产经营周转的授信产品。</text>
      </p>
    </view>
  </view>
  <view class="ad-text-box">
    <view class="ad-title1">服务对象</view>
    <view class="ad-content-box">
      <p class="ad-content ad-content-orange">个体工商户、小微企业</p>
    </view>
  </view>
  <view class="ad-text-box">
    <view class="ad-title">产品要素</view>
    <view class="intro-box">
      <view class="intro-line" style="padding-bottom: 0px">
        <image src="../../images/intro-no1.svg" class="intro-icon" alt="" style="padding-bottom: 0px"></image>
        <view class="intro-text intro-margin">额度：最高达600万元</view>
      </view>
      <view class="intro-line">
        <image src="../../images/intro-no2.svg" class="intro-icon" alt=""></image>
        <view class="intro-text intro-margin">期限：最长至60个月</view>
      </view>
      <view class="intro-line">
        <image src="../../images/intro-no3.svg" class="intro-icon" alt=""></image>
        <view class="intro-text intro-margin">年利率（单利）：最低至5.5%</view>
      </view>
      <view class="intro-line">
        <image src="../../images/intro-no4.svg" class="intro-icon" alt=""></image>
        <view class="intro-text intro-margin">担保方式：信用、保证、抵押均可</view>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

