        <image src="../../images/intro-no3.svg" class="intro-icon" alt=""></image>
        <view class="intro-text intro-margin">利率：最高不超过1年期LPR+50BP。</view>
      </view>
      <view class="intro-line">
        <image src="../../images/intro-no4.svg" class="intro-icon" alt=""></image>
        <view class="intro-text intro-margin">还款方式：按月付息，到期一次还本。</view>
      </view>
      <view class="intro-line">
        <image src="../../images/intro-no5.svg" class="intro-icon" alt=""></image>
        <view class="intro-text intro-margin">担保条件：无须动产或不动产抵质押。重点扶持人群无需反担保。</view>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>
  <view class="ad-text-box">
    <view class="ad-title">产品特色</view>
    <view class="intro-box">
      <view class="intro-line">
        <image src="../../images/intro-no1.svg" class="intro-icon" alt=""></image>
        <view class="intro-text intro-margin">额度高：个人最高<span class="orange">60万</span>，合伙经营单个企业合计最高<span class="orange">300万</span>。</view>
      </view>
      <view class="intro-line">
        <image src="../../images/intro-no2.svg" class="intro-icon" alt=""></image>
        <view class="intro-text intro-margin">贴息：符合条件审批后可享受政府贴息。</view>
      </view>
      <view class="intro-line">
        <image src="../../images/intro-no3.svg" class="intro-icon" alt=""></image>
        <view class="intro-text intro-margin">无须抵质押：无须动产或不动产抵质押。</view>
      </view>
      <view class="intro-line">
        <image src="../../images/intro-no4.svg" class="intro-icon" alt=""></image>
        <view class="intro-text intro-margin">还款灵活：可到期一次性还本。</view>
      </view>
      <view class="intro-line">
        <image src="../../images/intro-no5.svg" class="intro-icon" alt=""></image>
        <view class="intro-text intro-margin">阳光信贷：不与任何中介合作，除利息外不收取任何费用。</view>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>
  <view class="ad-text-box box-margin">
    <view class="ad-title">申请条件</view>
    <view class="intro-box">
      <view class="intro-line">
        <image src="../../images/intro-no1.svg" class="intro-icon" alt=""></image>
        <view class="intro-text intro-margin">真实经营：借款人在深圳注册企业，有具体经营项目，真实、合法经营。非重点扶持人群（深户及港澳台居民以外人群）经营企业登记注册时间需在3年内。</view>
      </view>
      <view class="intro-line">
        <image src="../../images/intro-no2.svg" class="intro-icon" alt=""></image>
        <view class="intro-text intro-margin">社保要求：借款人在其经营企业连续正常缴交6个月以上社保。（本市普通高校、职业学校、技工学校在校学生不受社保限制）</view>
      </view>
      <view class="intro-line">
        <image src="../../images/intro-no3.svg" class="intro-icon" alt=""></image>
        <view class="intro-text intro-margin">负债合理：除助学、扶贫、住房、购车贷款和一定金额以下小额消费贷款（含信用卡消费以外），借款人及其配偶无其他消费贷款。</view>
      </view>

      <view class="intro-line">
        <image src="../../images/intro-no4.svg" class="intro-icon" alt=""></image>
        <view class="intro-text intro-margin">反担保：非重点扶持人群需提供第三方信用等形式的反担保。</view>
      </view>
      <view class="intro-line">
        <image src="../../images/intro-no5.svg" class="intro-icon" alt=""></image>
        <view class="intro-text intro-margin">无不良信用记录。</view>
      </view>
      <view class="attention">
         注：具体以我行相关规定及政府创业担保贷款相关规定的要求为准。
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

  

  <view class="right-link" bindtap="next">
    马上申请
  </view>
</view>

